									<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-30023 size-full" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT.jpg" alt="" width="1830" height="1023" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT.jpg 1830w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT-300x168.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT-1024x572.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT-768x429.jpg 768w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT-1536x859.jpg 1536w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/07/IMG_5065_DS_EVENT-600x335.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1830px) 100vw, 1830px" /></p>								</div>
